_id>58826</s:story_id></item><item><title>Big 12’s Defensive Player of the Year Comes Up Big in Semifinal Victory Saturday Night</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/7/womens-basketball-big-12s-defensive-player-of-the-year-lifts-wvu-to-first-conference-title-game-appearance-since-2021</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/7/womens-basketball-big-12s-defensive-player-of-the-year-lifts-wvu-to-first-conference-title-game-appearance-since-2021</guid><category>Women's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Jordan Harrison" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/7/Harrison-Main.jpg" /><br /><br />KANSAS CITY – West Virginia needed the Big 12's Defensive Player of the Year to make the play of the game to advance to its first conference championship game since 2021.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/7/Harrison-Main.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/7/Harrison-Main.jpg"><media:title>Jordan Harrison</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/7/Harrison-Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 7 Mar 2026 23:34:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>9</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58824</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Places Fifth, Two Mountaineers Claim Bronze at Big 12 Championships</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/7/wrestling-west-virginia-places-fifth-two-mountaineers-claim-bronze-at-big-12-championships</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/7/wrestling-west-virginia-places-fifth-two-mountaineers-claim-bronze-at-big-12-championships</guid><category>Wrestling</category><description><![CDATA[<